1. Make a library of words to choose from

2. make a function to select a random word from that library

3. have that word appear in dashes until letter guessed

4. way for user to input their guess
    a. limit the amount of user guesses
    b. store incorrect guesses and make it so it doesnt count twice
    c. reveal correct guesses on word

5. message for end game
    a. you win
    b. you lose

6. log end game result for user to see 

7. make so process repeats
